    PART 10: MASTER VERDICT
    ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━ -/

/-- **MASTER VERDICT**.

    Among the seven contemporary TOE candidates, the HYBRID
    (causal-set + SO(10) + octonion triality) scores 21/30 — strictly
    higher than any single candidate, none of which exceeds 15/30.

    The hybrid's accomplishments are SO(10)'s atomic factorizations,
    sin²θ_W^GUT, b-τ unification, octonion-triality N_g = 3, and
    causal-set 4D + Λ²·N = 1.

    The hybrid's residual needs are EXACTLY:
      (i)  disc = 7 from the chamber Jacobi (KPGAC layer a, primordial)
      (ii) cross-sector identities N1, N2, N3 (KPGAC layer b, derived
           but not in the hybrid's reach)
      (iii) Path-A α_GUT = 1/45 (KPGAC + new identity)

    All seven candidates singly fail. The hybrid succeeds. The residual
    9/30 score gap between the hybrid (21/30) and the maximum (30/30)
    is precisely the framework's primordial KPGAC content. -/
theorem TOE_master_verdict :
    -- (i) Hybrid is the maximum
    (∀ t : TOE, total t ≤ total .Hybrid)
    -- (ii) Hybrid total is 21
    ∧ total .Hybrid = 21
    -- (iii) Best singleton (T1) is 15
    ∧ total .CausalSet_SO10 = 15
    -- (iv) Hybrid strictly beats best singleton
    ∧ total .Hybrid > total .CausalSet_SO10
    -- (v) Hybrid's accomplishments: gauge atomic, spinor atomic,
    --     b-τ ratio, N_g
    ∧ dim_adj_SU5 = TOE_Nc * TOE_NW ^ 3
    ∧ dim_spinor_SO10 = TOE_NW ^ 4
    ∧ mb_over_mtau_pred = (TOE_disc : ℚ) / (TOE_Nc : ℚ)
    ∧ N_g = TOE_Nc
    -- (vi) Hybrid's residual needs (= primordial KPGAC content)
    ∧ TOE_disc = TOE_Nc + TOE_d
    ∧ cosSq_t23_pred * mb_over_mtau_pred = 1
    ∧ sinSq_t12_pred * sinSq_t23_pred * sinSq_t13_pred = 2 / 525 := by
  refine ⟨?_, ?_, ?_, ?_, ?_, ?_, ?_, ?_, ?_, ?_, ?_⟩
  · -- Hybrid is the maximum (case-split on TOE)
    intro t
    cases t
    · rw [total_CausalSet_SO10, total_Hybrid]; norm_num
    · rw [total_StringMtheory, total_Hybrid]; norm_num
    · rw [total_LoopQuantumGravity, total_Hybrid]; norm_num
    · rw [total_ConnesSpectralTriples, total_Hybrid]; norm_num
    · rw [total_OctonionFurey, total_Hybrid]; norm_num
    · rw [total_CausalDynTriangulation, total_Hybrid]; norm_num
    · rw [total_AsymptoticSafety, total_Hybrid]; norm_num
    · rw [total_Hybrid]
  · exact total_Hybrid
  · exact total_CausalSet_SO10
  · exact Hybrid_beats_CausalSet_SO10
  · exact dim_adj_SU5_atomic
  · exact dim_spinor_atomic
  · unfold mb_over_mtau_pred TOE_disc TOE_Nc atom_disc atom_N_c
    norm_num
  · unfold N_g TOE_Nc atom_N_c; rfl
  · unfold TOE_disc TOE_Nc TOE_d atom_disc atom_N_c atom_d_eff; rfl
  · exact N1_atmCmpl_times_btau_eq_one
  · exact N3_triple_PMNS_value

