    The TOE ranking is FALSIFIABLE in three ways:

    (FAL1) A new measured cross-sector identity that ONLY one of the
           single candidates can derive — this would re-rank that
           candidate above the hybrid.

    (FAL2) A definitive observation that breaks SO(10) compatibility
